### =========================
### PATCH /users/:id
### Atualiza só email
### =========================
PATCH http://localhost:3333/users/{{bruninId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{bruninToken}}

{
  "name": "TESTE"
}



### =========================
### PATCH /users/:id
### Atualiza email + senha
